Restore Radiant Eyes and Total Self-Confidence with the Proven Formula Against Bags Under Eyes

Notre formule unique, développée avec une technologie avancée du collagène, est la solution la plus puissante et efficace pour réduire les poches, lisser les rides et restaurer une confiance en soi juvénile.

Curcuma

Le curcuma réduit l'inflammation et les poches sous les yeux grâce à ses puissants antioxydants. Il adoucit les poches, uniformise le teint et est essentiel pour un look frais et jeune naturellement.

Acide hyaluronique

L'acide hyaluronique hydrate en profondeur et repulpe la peau délicate sous les yeux. Il retient l'humidité, adoucit instantanément les rides fines et est essentiel pour maintenir la fermeté et l'élasticité sur le long terme.

Vitamine A (Rétinol)

Retinol accelerates cell renewal and stimulates collagen production. It softens wrinkles, strengthens skin structure and is essential for reversing visible signs of aging around the eyes.

Vitamin C

Vitamin C lightens dark circles and protects the skin from damage caused by free radicals. It stimulates collagen, evens out skin tone and is essential for a radiant and energetic area under the eyes.

Vitamin E

Vitamin E nourishes, protects and repairs delicate skin under the eyes. It prevents further damage, restores suppleness and is essential for long-lasting softness, smoothing and healthy eyes.

FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS

How to use BioEdge™?

Apply a small amount to the clean, dry skin under your eyes. Massage gently in upward motions until completely absorbed. For best results, use it twice a day. You will see a significant reduction in puffiness after just 5 minutes!

Who can use BioEdge™?

BioEdge™ is suitable for all skin types, including sensitive skin. It is ideal for anyone with problems with bags under the eyes, dark circles or fine lines, and looking for a gentle solution without syringes or fillers.

What does the box contain?

The packaging contains 3g treatment for bags under the eyes, easy to carry with you. It also includes clear instructions for getting the best results.

How long until you see results?

After just 5 minutes you will see the first results! Puffiness and dark circles will diminish, leaving your eyes instantly fresher and more alert.
